        "text": "=\ud83d\uddc2\ufe0f *Tax Document Processed*\n\n*Document:* {{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.formType }}\n*Tax Year:* {{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.taxYear }}\n\n\ud83d\udc64 *Taxpayer:* {{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.recipientName }}\n*Payer/Employer:* {{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.payerName }}\n\n\ud83d\udcb0 *Amounts:*\n\u2022 Total Income: ${{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.totalIncome }}\n\u2022 Federal Withheld: ${{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.federalWithheld }}\n\u2022 State Withheld: ${{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.stateWithheld }}\n\n\ud83d\udccb *Status:* {{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.status }}\n{{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.issues ? '\u26a0\ufe0f Issues: ' + $('Process Tax Form').item.json.issues : '\u2705 No issues' }}\n\n\ud83d\udd17 <https://drive.google.com/file/d/{{ $('Process Tax Form').item.json.fileId }}/view|View Document>",
